<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:71">Mission</h5>
<p class="u-textLg u-textGreyMedium no-margin-bottom padding-left-md padding-right-md" style="text-align:center;max-width:768px;margin:auto;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:46">
	The mission of The Salvation Army of Greater Charlotte is to meet human needs by offering hope, promoting dignity and providing opportunity – all in the name of Christ.
</p>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:3:46"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:4:60">Vision</h5>
<p class="u-textLg u-textGreyMedium no-margin-bottom padding-left-md padding-right-md" style="text-align:center;max-width:768px;margin:auto;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:5:64">
	To be a catalyst for upward mobility by providing a safe environment for those who need us most to live, learn and experience the love of Christ.
</p>
